<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>478</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zài hēi yè wǒ yǐ jīng kàn jiàn lí míng, zài hēi yè wǒ yǐ kàn jiàn chén xīng.
 zài hēi yè wǒ yào xiàng zhǔ áng shǒu, zàn měi de gē gèng jiā dòng tīng.
 zài hēi yè huā xiāng gèng nóng, zài hēi yè jiǎo bù gèng jiā jiān dìng.
 hēi yè de lù yǐ jīng méi yǒu jǐ chéng, nǐ qiè jì wù yào wèi zhǔ jǐn zhōng.</lyrics>
<title>zài hēi yè 迦南478</title>
</song>